              "free_text": [
                " thin  detector at the energy range 24-35 MeV,",
                " thick detector - 19-24 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The phototriton  cross  section  of  Li-6  has   been",
                " measured between 24 and 35 MeV photon energy.",
                "This work  complements  an  earlier  experiment which",
                " established  the  production  of  the   6Li(gamma,t)",
                " reaction by giant resonance photons and measured the",
                " cross section between 19 and 24 MeV.",
                "The phototriton   cross   section   of   6Li    falls",
                " monotonically  from  0.46(0.24)  mb  at  19  MeV  to",
                " 0.11(0.06) mb at 35 MeV.  The  integrated  (gamma,t)",
                " cross  section over this energy interval is 4.9(2.5)",
                " MeV*mb.  he measured bremsstrahlung weighted  cross",
                " section is 0.18(0.09) mb.",
                "Implications concerning    the   nuclear   size   are",
                " discussed."
              ]
            }
          ],
